remote: Write access to repository not granted.  
fatal: unable to access 'https://github.com/@username/repo.git/': The requested URL returned error: 403

o

remote: Repository not found.  
fatal: unable to access 'https://github.com/@username/repo.git/': The requested URL returned error: 403

Solucio:   
Selecciona Add a new account  
![][image1]  
Selecciona Sign in with a code  
![][image2]  
Copia el codi de 8 digits que apareix i clicka el link  
![][image3]

S’obrira una pestanya en el navegador, has de clickar Continue al compte que està associat al correu de l’institut, si no apareix clicka a Use different account i inicia sessio.

![][image4]  
Enganxa el codi copiat previament i clicka Continue  
![][image5]  
Clicka a Authorize git-ecosystem  
![][image6]  
Introdueix la teva contrasenya de github i clicka Confirm  
![][image7]

![][image8]
